{
  "stem": "25027.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she had about 15 to 20 children and preschoolers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that helped her survive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "While those people worked, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With a lot of those children, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was it what?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The religious were mainly the, the-- I'm looking for the word-- [LAUGHS] the organizers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we also had the [NON-ENGLISH], which organized youth for Palestine, and the shomrim.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they had many, many Jewish organizations.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] are we just discussing the Jewish part of it, or, in general, the whole city?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jewish community-- they had-- what do you call it-- where they organized self-- where the richer part of the Jewish community was helping with a hospital, with an old age home.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Mind you, when the war started, I was only 14 in 1939.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as a youngster, I paid no-- I didn't pay too much attention to that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in those days, the older people lived with the younger ones until we die-- [LAUGHS] until they passed away, if they had a chance to, to live that long.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and that was about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, grandfather used to get up very early in the morning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, Grandma and Grandfather-- yes, the two of them, and also an aunt, my mother's sister, her husband and three kids.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We lived all in the same house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It had four rooms.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother and I, and my grandfather, and grandmother, and our brother, my brother, lived on one side of the house.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was like it had a hallway in between.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "On one side, It had a old-fashioned kitchen with a oven on top.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it had one room where we slept, all slept in that one room.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, the grandparents slept in the kitchen part.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
